OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FDonald Trump has said the King "would
OL,8,Fhave probably helped" the US in its
OL,9,Fmilitary offensive against Iran.
OL,11,FThe US president made his remarks in
OL,12,Fthe Oval Office following Charles's
OL,13,Fspeech to Congress, in which the
OL,14,Fmonarch argued the need for a strong
OL,15,FNato and help for Ukraine, which have
OL,16,Fboth been criticised by the American
OL,17,Fleader.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@UO]
