OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777521848
OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FMr Trump has repeatedly lambasted the
OL,8,FUK for failing to join strikes against
OL,9,FTehran and branded Sir Keir Starmer as
OL,10,Fweak and indecisive.
OL,12,FThe president said: "The King is
OL,13,Ffantastic. We spent a lot of time
OL,14,Ftogether. We had a lot of talk. We
OL,15,Ftalked about this also, and he loves
OL,16,Fhis country, and he's a great king,
OL,17,Fand he's a great friend of mine.
OL,19,F"And I think if he were doing that, if
OL,20,Fthat were up to him, he would have
OL,21,Fprobably helped us with Iran."
OL,26,@tD@UOU{D@AOU}D@^O]
