OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FMr Trump added: "I think he's a
OL,8,Fphenomenal representative for his
OL,9,Fcountry. I think the people in the
OL,10,FUnited Kingdom should be proud."
OL,12,FMr Trump also used a speech on Tuesday
OL,13,Fduring the King's state visit to claim
OL,14,FCharles had agreed with him on the
OL,15,Fneed to prevent Tehran getting a
OL,16,Fnuclear bomb.
OL,26,@oD@QOUrD@`O]
