OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FConversations with the monarch are
OL,8,Fnormally kept private, but the
OL,9,Fpresident told a white-tie state
OL,10,Fbanquet: "We have militarily defeated
OL,11,Fthat particular opponent, and we're
OL,12,Fnever going to let that opponent ever
OL,13,F` Charles agrees with me, even more
OL,14,Fthan I do ` we're never going to let
OL,15,Fthat opponent have a nuclear weapon."
OL,26,@rD@JOUwD@eO]
