OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FIn response, a Buckingham Palace
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "The King is
OL,9,Fnaturally mindful of his Government's
OL,10,Flong-standing and well-known position
OL,11,Fon the prevention of nuclear
OL,12,Fproliferation."
OL,14,FAs part of the state visit, UK Foreign
OL,15,FSecretary Yvette Cooper and her US
OL,16,Fcounterpart Marco Rubio held talks in
OL,17,FWashington on the urgent need to
OL,18,Frestore the free movement of ships
OL,19,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@pD@TOUtD@OO]
