OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777521848
OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FThe Iran conflict and ensuing stand-
OL,8,Foff between the US and Tehran amid a
OL,9,Ffragile truce has effectively closed
OL,10,Fthe shipping lane, which is a major
OL,11,Froute for oil and gas supplies,
OL,12,Fsending energy prices soaring and
OL,13,Fdamaging the global economy.
OL,15,FFollowing the meeting between Mr Rubio
OL,16,Fand Ms Cooper, State Department
OL,17,Fspokesman Tommy Pigott said: "The
OL,18,Fsecretary and Foreign Secretary
OL,19,Fdiscussed the urgent need to restore
OL,20,Ffreedom of navigation in the Strait of
OL,21,FHormuz."
OL,26,@yD@^OU}D@HO]
