OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FIn a later tweet, Ms Cooper said she
OL,8,Fhad discussed both the Middle East and
OL,9,FEuro-Atlantic security with her US
OL,10,Fcounterpart, adding: "We discussed our
OL,11,Fshared focus on getting the Strait of
OL,12,FHormuz re-opened without Iranian tolls
OL,13,For restrictions."
OL,15,FIt came as First Sea Lord General Sir
OL,16,FGwyn Jenkins said the closure of the
OL,17,Fmaritime route and the international
OL,18,Fshock it has caused showed that "sea
OL,19,Fpower is vital".
