OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FThe strait, which was open prior to
OL,8,Fthe US and Israel launching strikes
OL,9,Fagainst Iran, has become the focus of
OL,10,Ftransatlantic tensions.
OL,12,FUS defence secretary Pete Hegseth
OL,13,Frecently dismissed efforts being led
OL,14,Fby the UK and France to ensure the
OL,15,Ffuture security of the waterway as
OL,16,F"silly" and said they should have
OL,17,F"less fancy conferences in Europe and
OL,18,Fget in a boat".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@GO]yD@AOUzD@NO]
