OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FHe said Europe needed the strait "much
OL,8,Fmore than we do" and that it was "much
OL,9,Fmore their fight than ours".
OL,11,FGiving evidence to Congress on
OL,12,FWednesday, Mr Hegseth said the
OL,13,FPentagon had "looked at all aspects"
OL,14,Fof the risk that Iran would block the
OL,15,Fshipping route.
