OL,3,CKing would have probably helped with
OL,4,Cmilitary strikes against Iran, says
OL,5,CTrump
OL,7,FAppearing with him, US military chief
OL,8,FGeneral Dan Caine said: "We always
OL,9,Foffer a full range of military options
OL,10,Fthat are carefully considered with the
OL,11,Fassociated risks with those options
OL,12,Fand the considerations therein."
OL,14,FEarlier, Mr Trump warned that Iran had
OL,15,F"better get smart" about a nuclear
OL,16,Fdeal as he appeared to threaten a
OL,17,Freturn to military action.
