OL,7,FThe president has justified the US-
OL,8,FIsraeli offensive, arguing it is aimed
OL,9,Fat halting Iran's nuclear weapons
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Mr Trump has also announced
OL,13,Fhe is considering cutting US troop
OL,14,Fnumbers in Germany, after the
OL,15,Fcountry's leader Friedrich Merz
OL,16,Fcriticised America over the Iran war
OL,17,Fand said it had been "humiliated" by
OL,18,FTehran.
